\f0 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Cleanroom Garments & Suits are specialized protective apparel designed to minimize particle contamination and electrostatic discharge (ESD) in cleanroom and static-sensitive manufacturing environments.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Widely used in semiconductor, electronics, PCB, pharmaceutical, optical, and precision manufacturing industries, cleanroom garments help maintain cleanliness standards while protecting sensitive products and production processes from dust, fibers, and human contamination.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Manufactured using low-lint and ESD-safe materials, our cleanroom garments provide comfort, durability, and reliable contamination control for cleanroom operations.\
